header.gameNote: PAC-12 MEN'S TOURNAMENT PRES. BY NEW YORK LIFE - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: California's Sam Singer cuts into the lane then scores off the glass early on for the Golden Bears.
videos.headline: Singer goes to the glass to score for Cal

videos.description: Utah's Lorenzo Bonam drives through the lane and throws down a dunk.
videos.headline: Bonam slams home a one-handed dunk

videos.description: California's Jabari Bird drives and misses a lay-in attempt but grabs his own rebound and scores.
videos.headline: Bird keeps focus after missed shot to lay it in

videos.description: California's Jabari Bird is fouled as he fights through traffic and scores on a layup.
videos.headline: Bird gets the tough layup and-1 to fall

videos.description: Cal's Jabari Bird hits a wide open 3-pointer from the top of the key to extend California's lead.
videos.headline: Bird connects on an open 3-pointer

videos.description: California's Charlie Moore drives in the lane and splits two defenders on his way to making an impressive layup.
videos.headline: Moore splits defenders and makes an acrobatic layup

videos.description: California's Jabari Bird catches a pass from Sam Singer then connects on a 3-pointer from the right wing.
videos.headline: Bird drills catch and shoot three from the right wing for Cal

videos.description: Utah's David Collette drives in and is fouled as he makes his shot with the help of a lucky bounce.
videos.headline: Collette gets the and-1 to drop from high off the glass

videos.description: California's Charlie Moore banks in a 3-pointer as the shot clock winds down.
videos.headline: Moore hits unbelievable off-balanced 3-pointer

videos.description: California's Charlie Moore attacks the paint, spins and hits a floater with his left hand for the bucket.
videos.headline: Moore spins and scores in the lane for the Golden Bears

videos.description: Utah's Kyle Kuzma hits a three in transition after California's Charlie Moore misses a layup at the other end.
videos.headline: Kuzma cuts the Cal lead to two

videos.description: Utah's Kyle Kuzma cuts California's lead down to one with under seven seconds to go after drilling a three from deep.
videos.headline: Kuzma connects from way downtown with 6.7 seconds to go

videos.description: Utah's Sedrick Barefield misses a potential game-tying 3-pointer as the game clock expires. California holds on to win 78-75.
videos.headline: Utah comes up short in final seconds
